                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18230115-165-off897 t18230115-165-crimeloc899"></join>. On the 17th of December, the prisoner was at work on my premises, and something being wrong on the adjoining roof, I sent them to repair it. In the evening the officer<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182301150053"></xptr>brought me some lead, which I compared with the roof and it corresponded with what was missing there. The house belonged to my mother-in-law, Isabella Guson. 
